name: WMFG Special Edition - A Window of Imagination

metadata.name: A Window of Imagination - Floating Clouds
metadata.description:
Going to places where my feet takes me, I often times had the pleasure to look down at the clouds and stare out from the small airplane windows. The view sometimes takes my breath and I wonder what is really above us and far beyond where we have our feet on. 

This is the Window of Imagination, Floating Clouds. 

Follow WMFG for special airdrops eligible for holders: https://linktr.ee/wmfg
